<main class="artic-word-main">
    <h2 class="artic-word-heading">ITSM Short Description Guidelines</h2>
    <p>
        In the ITSM system, the Short Description is a concise summary of your key request or issue.<br>
        Please fill in the main point of your request so that the IT team can quickly understand and assign the task.
    </p>
    <hr />
    <h3>When writing a short description, please keep in mind:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>✅ Use clear and concise language to state your main need or issue.</li>
        <li>✅ Avoid long sentences or unnecessary background information.</li>
        <li>✅ If you need to add more details, please provide them in the detailed description section.</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />
    <h3>Examples:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Computer won't start</li>
        <li>Cannot connect to company WiFi</li>
        <li>Need to install specific software</li>
        <li>Requesting a new employee account</li>
        <li>Product inventory information is incorrect</li>
        <li>Cannot export report to PDF</li>
        <li>Email sending failed</li>
        <li>Requesting a laptop for a new team member</li>
        <li>Need service account for project XYZ</li>
        <li>Requesting remote access for a contractor</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />
    <h3>Note:</h3>
    <p>If you have any issues filling out the short description, please contact the IT department for assistance.</p>
</main>
